		</div>
		<div class="mt-2">
			An initiative of the Middle East and North Africa Union of Seventh-day Adventists.<br>
		</div>
		<div class="mt-2">
			<a href="/feedback">Feedback</a> | <a href="/feedback">Bug report</a>
		</div>
	</footer>
